  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary ITP has wide heterogenous biology, presentation and response to therapy.

      The immune-genetic assessment of ITP may help to identify differences among patients with ITP
      and optimize the therapeutic choice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
